70|MINIGAME|10|This exercise will test your chef's concentration skills.
71|MINIGAME|11|The ball will move in a figure-eight pattern across the rings.
72|MINIGAME|12| Click the STOP button when the ball is closest to the innermost ring.
73|MINIGAME|13| If you time it right, your chef will increase his concentration skills.
74|MINIGAME|14|But don't take too long - remember, the timer is ticking!
75|MINIGAME|15|This little exercise will test your chef's precision when preparing recipes.
76|MINIGAME|16|Time it so that when you click the STOP button the bar rests as close to the center point as possible.
77|MINIGAME|17| The closer the bar is to the center, the more your chef's skill will improve.
78|MINIGAME|18|Just make sure you keep an eye out for the timer, and click the STOP button before the timer reaches zero!
79|MINIGAME|19|This exercise will test your chef's organizational abilities in the kitchen.
80|MINIGAME|20|There are six boxes, with the %1j{numbers 1-6|letters A-F} written on them.
81|MINIGAME|21| However, the %1j{numbers|letters} are jumbled out of order.
82|MINIGAME|22| Click on the boxes in order before the timer reaches zero, and your chef will experience an increase in his organizing abilities.
83|MINIGAME|23|Remember, you have to click on the %1j{numbers|letters} in order!
